{
  "stem": "4187.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Again, I suppose in vain, I'll try and explain what this means when you're, for the first time, truly, in your life, faced with this sort of inhumanity.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's-- this is over 50 years ago now, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was in 1944.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And to me, I can see the expression on her face.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It just burns into your memory, because the shock is so horrendous that it'll never leave you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there is things that, to this day, to me-- you know, I know perfectly well that this has caused this, and this, and this, and this, because the shock to one's system was such that it was forever.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It just burnt in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there it stays, never to be moved again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyway, we were eventually-- not eventually, but fairly quickly then-- out of-- of cattle trucks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had to be-- we-- we to jump down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And of course, these old people-- because there was some very old people that had to be-- no one was helped down, as you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They just had to make the best of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was just awful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And of course, opposite, right opposite us, we could see all these armed SS, armed to the teeth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because now, we got the SS.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That's really when we first start-- and-- and every single one of them had, naturally, not-- not-- not rifles, pistols.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Many of them had these huge, vicious-looking dogs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You could tell that these dogs will eat you up in no time at all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They all had whips.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So it was like a scene out of an inferno.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were-- we got off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were told to stand five in a line, which was always.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was always five in a line.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
